FBIS3-33914 "drnes022_a_94007" FBIS-NES-94-022 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Feb 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Ministry Condemns Event LD0102232394 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 2200 GMT 1 Feb 94 LD0102232394 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] In a statement issued today, the Ministry of Communications strongly condemned the cowardly assassination that has recently grieved the entire community of journalists overseas and considers it as a practice alien to Algeria's traditions. [passage omitted]: The statement made clear that the two reporters went to the Casbah quarter without taking into consideration the instructions of the authorities. It added that a police patrol had come across them yesterday at Bab El Oued and advised them not to go to some areas without taking the necessary precautions. The two reporters who came to Algeria to cover the national conference wanted to complete their work by doing some field investigations. [passage omitted]
